Class AttributeStorage

java.lang.Object
jadx.core.dex.attributes.AttributeStorage
Direct Known Subclasses:
EmptyAttrStorage
public class AttributeStorage extends Object
Storage for different attribute types: 1. flags - boolean attribute (set or not) 2. attribute - class instance associated with attribute type.
